00:04:54.150 --> 00:04:55.720 align:middle line:90%
It's an illusion.

00:04:55.720 --> 00:04:57.300 align:middle line:84%
>> Well, it's an
illusion in physics,

00:04:57.300 --> 00:05:00.360 align:middle line:84%
and it's also an illusion
with regard to our psychology

00:05:00.360 --> 00:05:02.280 align:middle line:90%
and our personal experience.

00:05:02.280 --> 00:05:06.990 align:middle line:84%
