photons with a prism,

00:05:17.760 --> 00:05:19.530 align:middle line:84%
if you look at
light with a prism,

00:05:19.530 --> 00:05:22.350 align:middle line:84%
you'll see that the prism
breaks the light down

00:05:22.350 --> 00:05:23.820 align:middle line:90%
into beautiful colors.

00:05:23.820 --> 00:05:27.420 align:middle line:84%
