00:05:53.600 --> 00:05:56.530 align:middle line:84%
This is also
ancient Vedic ideas.

00:05:56.530 --> 00:06:01.180 align:middle line:84%
You know, what we see
has no intrinsic meaning,

00:06:01.180 --> 00:06:03.370 align:middle line:84%
