bring to it with regard

00:06:03.370 --> 00:06:06.400 align:middle line:84%
to our personality, our
preconceptions, and our views,

00:06:06.400 --> 00:06:09.970 align:middle line:84%
and our scientific
instruments is a determinant

00:06:09.970 --> 00:06:12.580 align:middle line:90%
of what we get to see.

00:06:12.580 --> 00:06:16.270 align:middle line:84%
